## 📁 Project Structure

```bash
house_price_prediction/
├── model/
│   ├── Real_sate_dataclining (1).ipynb    # Data cleaning & modeling notebook
│   ├── banglore_home_prices_model.pickle  # Trained ML model
│   ├── columns.json                        # Feature columns info
├── server/
│   ├── util.py                             # Model loading & prediction utilities
│   └── artifacts/                          # Folder with model artifacts
├── .idea/                                  # IDE configurations
├── .gitignore                              # Git ignore settings
└── README.md                               # Project documentation
